Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:45.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Five million dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:52.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Five million dollars were stolen on my territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:56.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no way I can just let this slide, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:01.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Find the culprit and drag him before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...you can kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:16.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's always been my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to have a mountain of burgers in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and stuff myself until \Nmy stomach wouldn't take them any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:28.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, Cal. About what you said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:31.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You saw who killed Judy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was wondering what I'll do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:37.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:41.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you really avenge Judy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:42.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:46.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They used machine guns, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:49.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you don't seem that strong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:56.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't be trusted, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not really the one who would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:03.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was planning to ask my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:05.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have such a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:11.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I may not look it, but I know a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we know what the murderer looks like and what he wears,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can have my friend look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:22.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, the one who shot her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:24.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to see it for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:25.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to see it when you kill the guy who killed Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Reiji. Let me see your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:32.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:37.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why? Take me with you when you ask your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:38.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:42.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not a world ordinary people can associate with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:43.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No means no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:51.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll ask her if you can see her or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright then, let's talk about it when we see your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:20.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People like her can't be contacted right away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will arrange it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's talk about it again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:27.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:30.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The rent on Judy's room was piling up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so I got kicked out this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can I stay at your place tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:49.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How is it going, Lizzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:54.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is the investigation proceeding smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:58.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom has the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm checking out another lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:03.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm expecting some meaningful information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:15.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who ruined my deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:21.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Goudou clan's existence is indispensable to strengthen Inferno's position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This sort of incident will not topple me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So this is your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:35.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's kind of lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's more than enough to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:46.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the leftover burgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not eating them would be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:52.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me you're going to stay here until you finish them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your bedroom is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The bed is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Were you living here with someone before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just a hunch I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:15.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:21.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can I use the shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I just have to act like that "friend" of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, do me the favor please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:35.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fine by me. Having you owe me a favor isn't bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, do you really think that girl is any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What an unreliable answer you give me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, I forgot to bring a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:22.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never thought the venerable and almighty Phantom would be toyed with by a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Letting her stay in your room doesn't mean you can do strange-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He cut me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:43.52,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing sneaking around in someone else's back yard, Lizzie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:47.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:51.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, she said we can see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She will contact us tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Say, Reiji. Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:14.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have your parents passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:24.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I ran away from the worst father there ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Judy found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:31.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If she hadn't, I'd probably be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that's why you said you're her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:38.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. She was the only family I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But now she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:48.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:54.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do now that Judy is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've been through it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:05.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:10.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even death comes in many forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:14.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Some leave behind deep anguish for those alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:17.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and some die without anyone to grieve for them, slowly forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:22.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Judy is happy, since she has you to cry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:25.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:52.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Where should I go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I don't know anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is the witness in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:37.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is a pretty dull place to stay in, isn't it, Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:38.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't put on airs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:46.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I saw Lizzie sneaking around and searching for some rats downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and heard some pretty interesting stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me talk to the little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll make her spill the beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She knows nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:13.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:19.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}An untrained girl wouldn't be able to see anything in that dark alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:22.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She lied when she said she saw the shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:55.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'd protect her even if it means spilling blood, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to meet her even more now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:10.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So everything is just as I suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:13.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You and Claudia are cooking something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ten o'clock tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:28.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll have you tell it all in front of McGwire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then we'll know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:33.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...who the traitor is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:38.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I couldn't talk my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But isn't this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How will you convince them tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll make excuses somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So is she really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She doesn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:58.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.52,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't know anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}do you, Cal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.58,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shall I hear your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:50.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Judy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Judy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:13:59.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know anything after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you saw through my lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:11.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That man just now was Isaac Wisemel, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The leader of the Bloodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:14.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did you cover for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:24.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone called you Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard about it from Judy's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.62,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're the one who has been killing gang members all over America.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're a real assassin, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're an assassin, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Assassin, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Those Yakuzas brought this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I counted five million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:02.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You stole it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:09.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't even use one cent of this dirty money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was looking for someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone I could hire with this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:18.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji, you're Phantom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:26.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please kill everyone with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:30.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The people who were there in the alley yesterday, the ones who fired guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and those who were supposed to receive this money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:39.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kill everyone who killed Judy without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:47.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to estimate the price for the killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:48.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's talk about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:55.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:12.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The situation is going bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The assailant is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Only the five million dollars were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:23.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If the organization found this money, I couldn't make excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:28.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Kill everyone who killed Judy without exception.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:35.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can I balance both Cal's and the organization's demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's the meaning of this, Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't explain it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:02.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we discuss this matter in private, it will arouse Wisemel's suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll talk about everything in front of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let us hear your explanation, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}First, I would like to clear up a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh? Misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:21.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's true I gave shelter to the girl who witnessed the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:26.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She was just passing by though and got dragged into it. She knows nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can you be so sure of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm capable of seeing such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A stupid excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It sounds like that to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:40.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's completely meaningless without proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you use drugs to make her talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Any recorded data?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:48.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}None.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:53.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So in short you're telling us to trust your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:54.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:58.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drop it already, Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.05,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miss McCunnen, do you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:08.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have my reasons not to use drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it for the same reasons you pointed your gun at Isaac?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let us hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:19.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't want to break her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Humanism at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:22.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:28.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I saw a different potential inside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And I didn't want to ruin that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She has a rare resourcefulness about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:39.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can call it a talent if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:42.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The yearning to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hellish solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A spectre with nowhere to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Talent".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard the same word a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:04.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, you want to train the girl into another hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:15.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She might become a skilled \Nright hand to me in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Any proof of this girl's talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't mess around, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This isn't something I can explain through words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:32.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A human who has his eyes clouded by suspicion might not be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}One question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you really wish for a new assistant that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:45.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you saying there are problems with the teamwork between Lizzie and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:50.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, we have problems alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom and me contrast too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:57.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom is a genius, yet I'm just an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:03.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If there is a different partner he set his eyes on,\N I'd trade places with her any day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:10.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About that prostitute, Judy Devens, that died along with the Yakuzas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:13.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you positive she has nothing to do with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I left no stone unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think, Isaac?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you telling me to accept this, Ray?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you cannot give rise to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:37.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know what happens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:40.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:45.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, let's see how skillful you can shape her to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:50.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was an interesting playact, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ya can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ya can't fucking fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You damn watchdog of a fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:03.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was my fault to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:07.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:09.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:13.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't want to create another of your lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.21,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just a way to protect her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But now that you've sung her praises,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:21.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you will be held responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:26.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the end, nothing is solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The assailant,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.16,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the five million dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}avenging Judy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:38.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's probably a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But is it okay to let her walk the same path I took?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But is it okay to let her walk the same path I took?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But is it okay to let her walk the same path I took?
